{"tid":181793,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪被指秘密拍拖5年","createTime":"2017-04-01T00:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T09:30:36.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6b830204781e9266f7ccaaf746a11cf920135a","tid":181793,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170331/large/31ec4p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F31ec4p1.jpg&h=b3471e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪日前出席手機活動時表示沒拖拍，但本報接獲讀者爆料，指朱千雪跟一位在澳洲讀醫的Justin Ng拍拖5年，而Justin是有家底之人，其父五年前在香格里拉集團做執行董事，現為老牌茶莊「祺棧茶行」老闆。在朱千雪facebook的朋友名單中，連Justin父親及胞弟也是朋友，可見她與Justin關係密切。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/y6cmiro0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fy6cmiro0&h=89e92935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uqb79e4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuqb79e4d&h=1aa2e1dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據本報了解，Justin其實是朱千雪眾多追求者之一，雖然身在澳洲讀醫，但跟她一直保持聯絡。不過，現時在香港城市大學修讀法律博士學位的朱千雪正忙於考試，根本沒時間拍拖，看來Justin要繼續耐心等候。"},{"pid":"765adb0870ee4da7531593fa05036a11ce76b905","tid":181793,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好失落..."},{"pid":"7850cba8fb6b312aeac44acdb63d50bce3925e14","tid":181793,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/waspbv1r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwaspbv1r&h=e4810e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aj2ohstr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faj2ohstr&h=52fed601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4qkdy6wf\" data-thumb